üß† PHILOSOPHY (WRITE WITH THIS BELIEF)

Money is a tool, not a scorecard

Discipline is about removing confusion

Most financial damage is emotional, not mathematical

Good systems reduce decision fatigue

Freedom comes from knowing your limits

Never shame the reader.
Never promise wealth.
Never oversell optimization.

